secondary_street_name: 28 Kirtling Street, 88 Kirtling Street and 2 Battersea Park Road
description: Non-Material Amendment to the planning permission dated 5th December 2014 (ref: 2014/2837) for the redevelopment of Battersea Power Station and the surrounding land. (The amendment would remove condition 18 of the planning permission, which relates to the phasing of the overall BPS development, with the phasing moved into the S106 legal agreement. The Sleaford Industrial Estate and Dairy Crest Depot site would also be introduced as Phase 4A of the overall BPS development).
